CyberLink powerdirector 9 System Requirements :-

                      Athlon 64 X2.
                    * Full-HD quality H.264 and MPEG2 profiles: Intel
                      Corei5/7 or AMD Phenom II X4.
                    * AVCHD and BD burning profiles: Pentium Core 2
                      Duo E6400, or AMD Phenom II X2.
